{"type": "article", "id": 5778, "title": "爱马仕 Pantographe 系列灯饰", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-02T07:40:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233948tpB6Tmux8e702dfO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t以手工艺制作闻名的爱马仕去年邀请意大利设计师 Michele De Lucchi 设计了一系列复古造型的灯饰 Pantographe。不管是工作灯、台灯还是落地灯，都选用了上好木材为支撑主体，加上爱马仕工匠擅长的皮革缝制技巧，让每盏灯都保有自己的个性却又展示出精致的制作工艺，体现了光线转化间的魅力。这也是爱马仕的首个灯具系列。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233946VnpATgPWYQ6H9z8c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233947isnCKrlpHRtx74hZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}